liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: What a ball! 152kph inswinger, straight through the gate, Khawaja had no chance and has to go for 13! He even looks shocked at how quick that was. WHAT A BALL! You're not stopping that too easily and that is what pace can do. Mark Wood has deserved that, bowling at that speed, for that amount of time, with that degree of accuracy is extraordinary. What a way to go to drinks and bring the ABC Sport equivalent of Mark Wood into the attack, Jon Healy.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: BOWLED HIM! KHAWAJA IS OUT!

children.content: What a ball! 152kph inswinger, straight through the gate, Khawaja had no chance and has to go for 13! He even looks shocked at how quick that was.

Mark Wood has deserved that, bowling at that speed, for that amount of time, with that degree of accuracy is extraordinary.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Brilliant start for England! Broad is off revving up the Western Terrace, who roar in delight! Warner didn't need to play at that, but he nibbled at it outside off, and it's a great catch at second slip by Zak Crawley!
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: EDGED! TAKEN! WARNER IS OUT!

children.content: Broad is off revving up the Western Terrace, who roar in delight!
